    "Descriptive-correlational design tries to describe or explain the relationship between two or more variables.",
    "It is done through collecting and analyzing data on at least two variables to find out if there is a connection between them.",
    "Moreover, the study utilized the qualitative research method to discover and describe the observable behaviors and activities of students towards different situations.",
    "This study was conducted at Ipil National High School (INHS), Gonzaga East District for the academic year 2023-2024.",
